rmal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/634452558"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIqKP97o6LnrgmEAMaCTEwMzI2Nzk5NCDRo9+rBjAAON4BQAVyCTYzNDQ1MjU1OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1734549498.204665", "card_id": "Q_6844291020", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2024 有哪些让你看一次笑一次的综艺名场面？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-08b39004307f636e59684c5e705d0001_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6844291020"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIqKP97o6LnrgmEAMaCTExMjM0NTY0NyDp6fS6BjAAOClABnIKNjg0NDI5MTAyMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1734549498.204833", "card_id": "Q_6738858957", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么感觉「电动汽车的续航焦虑」被提及的越来越少了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-787cb06e4bfd942d1505258046fbceb7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6738858957"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIqKP97o6LnrgmEAMaCTExMjMyNDQzMiCRwu66BjAAOH1AB3IKNjczODg1ODk1N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1734549498.204986", "card_id": "Q_6982952605", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 54}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "统计局数据显示，前 11 月新建商品房销售额 85125 亿元，同比下降 19.2%，有哪些影响因素？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "12 月 16 日，国家统计局发布 2024 年 1—11 月份全国房地产市场基本情况。 新建商品房销售和待售情况方面，1—11 月份，新建商品房销售面积 86118 万平方米，同比下降 14.3%，其中住宅销售面积下降 16.0%。新建商品房销售额 85125 亿元，下降 19.2%，其中住宅销售额下降 20.0%。前 11 个月，全国固定资产投资同比增长 3.3％"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ae49c513015e4aae0ad9324becf711dd_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6982952605"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIqKP97o6LnrgmEAMaCTExMjM3MzM4NSDmnv66BjAAOLoBQAhyCjY5ODI5NTI2MDV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1734549498.205369", "card_id": "Q_7062461362", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 172}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "李亚鹏进军白酒行业，对此你如何评价？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近期，李亚鹏频频在自己的抖音账号上为一款名为「拎壶冲」的白酒「打 Call」。同时，他还单独开设了一个酒品垂类账户「李亚鹏·拎壶冲冲冲」，该账号也为这款酒做过宣传。 《每日经济新闻·将进酒》记者注意到，拎壶冲由贵州酱酒集团出品，据称历经了三年酝酿。拎壶冲的 3 款产品售价主要在 398～1298 元。据海报等信息，李亚鹏担任拎壶冲产品推荐官，9 月时在他的视频直播间首发。但是，从目前产品在直播间中的销量来看，才刚刚起步。 作为无数人银幕记忆的「令狐冲」，李亚鹏曾尝试房地产、直播带货等各种跨界，然而其商业之路并不平坦。在 2022 年因投资地产失利，「欠债 4000 万案终审败诉」后，李亚鹏入局直播带货。他不仅售卖茶叶，还推出了自家品牌「书院造」。2024 年以来每月直播次数在 20 次左右，不可谓不努力。今年 2 月，李亚鹏直播时聊到收入的话题，失声痛哭，边哭边说自己已经还了多年的债，还哭诉连续吃了一周的外卖。 那么，与「令狐冲」IP 深度绑定的「拎壶冲」能成为下一个白酒爆款吗？行业内卷之下，又有多少粉丝愿意为情怀买单？ 12 月 16 日下午，《每日经济新闻·将进酒》记者拨打贵州酱酒集团公开电话，欲了解详情，同时也在李亚鹏抖音账号下留言，希望取得回应，但截至记者发稿，均暂无回应。 投资上亿、对标茅台？李亚鹏进军白酒行业：直播仅卖出百单"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6e8265f78de540887eaee407d2c551b9_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7062461362"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIqKP97o6LnrgmEAMaCTExMjM4OTI1NSDiz4K7BjAAOO4BQAlyCjcwNjI0NjEzNjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1734549498.206075", "card_id": "Q_6820300201", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在新能源汽车高度发展的形势下，燃油车还有未来吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在新能源汽车高度发展的形势下，燃